<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="glare-vi">glare <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɡleə(r)/    美 /ɡler/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>发出刺眼的光：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sun glared out of the blue sky.
太阳在蔚蓝色的天空中发出耀眼的光芒。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>瞪眼；怒目而视：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Noah was annoyed but he didn't shout; he just <strong>glared at</strong> me silently.
诺亚很恼火，但是他没大喊大叫，只是默默地瞪着我。</p></div></div>